{"tid":767793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"討論發夢 好耐無試過發夢咁開心","createTime":"2018-08-04T22:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T12:57:17.000Z","uid":143023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2fbc44fc8160129fcc8aa0332921c29e7eb42f","tid":767793,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T22:21:07.000Z","msg":"剛醒<br />\n仲好記得<br />\n個夢 係我經歷咗好多事 女主記番起係我<br />\n之後 個種興奮 同 幸福<br />\n<br />\n發夢 好難得咁開心 真係好幸福 唔想完<br />\n因為我好似 歷咗個夢咁<br />\n好有實感<br />\n<br />\n想知有咩方法可以 易發到好夢<br />\n<br />\n真係好開心 剛剛發到的幸福夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7a56e5fd3e2e9f4aed2b9070ebc9c7d8af1293","tid":767793,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:14:41.000Z","msg":"發春夢時最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7ad2bd70c05298e557932fb2d49863cceb5e48","tid":767793,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7a56e5fd3e2e9f4aed2b9070ebc9c7d8af1293","tid":767793,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T23:14:41.000Z","msg":"發春夢時最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T00:25:47.000Z","msg":"我個夢真係 好似戲咁 苦盡甘來 好有實感<br />\n唔係春夢咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n好開心 發完後"},{"pid":"9b3dc950963d5912aa918822409b4934de794c3e","tid":767793,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"做左廿年人都好似無發過好夢<br />\n多數都係怪夢/無厘頭夢/惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b15f6e1b91a32c34093aa00bf6e5b9b1ebcaf9","tid":767793,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b3dc950963d5912aa918822409b4934de794c3e","tid":767793,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:47:52.000Z","